# [ACE](../wg/ace.html)

## Summary
The ACE Working Group met at IETF 126 to discuss the status and updates of its active documents, as well as a new proposal for post-quantum security in group communications. Key topics included the progression of the CoAP Publish-Subscribe profile to Shepherd review, updates to the Short Distribution Chain (SDC) workflow and parameter definitions, and significant progress on the EDHOC-OSCORE and Group OSCORE profiles. Additionally, a new mechanism was presented for supporting Key Encapsulation Mechanisms (KEM) in the OSCORE Group Manager interface to address post-quantum migration.

---

