### 2. CoAP Publish-Subscribe Profile
* **Presenter:** Marco Tiloca
* **Draft:** [draft-ietf-ace-coap-pubsub-profile](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-ace-coap-pubsub-profile/)
* **Slides:** [20260720-ace-coap-pubsub-profile](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-ace-20260720-ace-coap-pubsub-profile-00)

#### Discussion:
* Marco Tiloca presented the updates in version 05. The draft specifies an application profile of the ACE framework for group key distribution using CoAP Pub-Sub.
* Since the working group last call (WGLC) completed, updates (v04 and v05) addressed feedback aligned with analogous comments from the IESG evaluation of other group key distribution profiles (specifically regarding editorial clarifications and requirements).
* Crucially, the draft was updated to align with the latest editorial revisions of the core CoAP Pub-Sub architecture specification, which has now been submitted to the IESG.
* Two missing IANA parameter registration sections were identified and have been successfully added.
* **Status:** The document is stable and ready for the Write-up and Shepherd review.

