## Decisions and Action Items

### Decisions
* **[draft-ietf-ace-coap-pubsub-profile]** Agreed that the draft is stable and ready to progress to Shepherd Write-up, as all blocking issues and external dependencies are resolved.
* **[draft-ietf-ace-edhoc-oscore-profile]** Agreed to simplify the reverse flow by only allowing the access token in EDHOC Message 4 (EAD4), removing the Message 2 (EAD2) option.
* **[draft-ietf-ace-group-oscore-profile]** Approved the simplified RS-side access token binding mechanism and the introduction of Token Series IDs for dynamic access right updates.

